de.systemagmbh.interfaces.server
Interface ISysMessageService

All Superinterfaces:
ISysComponent
All Known Implementing Classes:
DummyISysMessageService
public interface ISysMessageService
extends ISysComponent

The interface ISysMessageService defines the functionality that a service class must provide to be registered at the ISysBus with addService(). This interface will replace the interface ISysService that gets and returns Strings.
